Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 43rd Weekly Dose of Optimism.
We got Advance Market Commitments putting their money where their mouth is,=
 novel approaches to fighting climate change, promising brain research on b=
oth Alzheimer=E2=80=99s and major depressive disorder, and some space cells=
=2E Big week.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.=20
Today=E2=80=99s Not Boring is brought to you by=E2=80=A6Tegus [ https://sub=
